entries.npc_1: Welcome to Jabba's town house.  What can be done for you?  Hmm?
entries.npc_2: Hmm?  Yes.  Of course he does.  Why?  Shouldn't he?  Hmm?
entries.npc_7: On occasion.  Mostly we do business from here, and keep Jabba's guests very comfortable.  Hmm.
entries.npc_3: I'm sorry, but Master is away at the Palace.
entries.player_5: You know that's actually a monastery, right?
entries.npc_4: The old B'omarr monastery?  Hmm...Believe me, it is Jabba's Palace.  No more, and no less.
entries.npc_8: Oh, those spider droids? Hmm? Believe me when I tell you that they know their place there.
entries.player_8: He stole it.  What if someone steals it from him?
entries.npc_9: I would feel pity for anyone who thought they could take the Palace back away from the master.  Hmm?  Oh yes.  Much pity.
entries.npc_5: Hmm?  We don't expect the Master.  He comes and goes at his pleasure.  We strive only to serve.  Hmm.
entries.player_9: Why do you keep saying Hm?
entries.npc_10: It's a nervous tick.  Hmm.  I assure you.  Nothing more.  Hmm.
entries.player_10: Well, I guess I'll go check at the palace then.
entries.npc_11: Hmm.  And that is where you shall find him.
